Collection Description: Physical science is the study of matter and energy. Physical science can be divided into chemistry and physics. Chemistry is the study of matter and energy at the scale of atoms and molecules. Physics is the study of matter and energy at all scales—from the tiniest particles of matter to the entire universe.
